Package: ecomsUDG.Raccess
Depends: downscaleR.java, downscaleR, R(>= 3.0.0)
Type: Package
Title: The R interface for accessing the ECOMS User Data Gateway
Version: 2.2-1
Date: 5 Aug 2014
Author: Santander Meteorology Group <http://www.meteo.unican.es>
Maintainer: Joaquin Bedia <bediaj@unican.es>
BugReports: https://github.com/SantanderMetGroup/ecomsUDG.Raccess/issues
URL: http://meteo.unican.es/ecoms-udg
Description: This package enables homogenized, user-friendly access to hindcast and other climate databases remotely stored at the ECOMS User Data Gateway, allowing the retrieval of manageable dimensional slices from large climate datasets. The use of this package requires prior registration in the ECOMS-UDG (go to <http://meteo.unican.es/ecoms-udg/DataServer/Registration>).
License: GPL (>= 3)
